snippet.title: Chase HQ 2 Arcade - Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Full gameplay video of Taito's Chase HQ 2 arcade driving machine for the first time on Youtube! Footage is captured straight from the gameboard in-house at Highway Entertainment, and is a full playthrough of this rare arcade game.

For further information on this driving arcade machine please visit http://www.arcade-game-sales.com/search.html?query=chase+hq
